{"word":"G4692 - σπεύδω - speúdō - spyoo'-do - Haste unto","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σπεύδω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">speúdō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">spyoo'-do</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Haste unto</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"தீவிரப்பட்டு, சீக்கிரமாய், தீவிரமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. to hasten"},{"paragraph":"2. to desire earnestly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably strengthened from <a href=\"#/G4228 - πούς - poús - pooce/4228\">G4228</a>; to &ldquo;speed&rdquo; (&ldquo;study&rdquo;), that is, <i>urge</i> on (diligently or earnestly); by implication to <i>await</i> eagerly: - (make, with) haste unto.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}